<P>Expences on 25 tons weight, from Philadelphia to Knoxville, as per letter W 10714 dols.</P>
<P>In favor of the Mi&s;&s;i&s;&s;ippi com|merce, on 25 tons weight 8,064 dolls.</P>
<P>From the mouth of Ohio river, to Na&s;hville on Cumberland, in the State of Tenne&s;&s;ee, is about 250 miles&mdash;time of pa&s;&s;ing to and from the &s;aid ports, with a boat of 25 tons burthen, will be about 25 days; with the a&s;&s;i&s;tance of 10 hands at one dollar per day, is 250 dollars.</P>
<P>To the mouth of the Mi&s;&s;i&s;&s;ippi, as per letter V 2,000 dolls.</P>
<P>Total expence, on 25 tons weight, from the mouth of Mi&s;&s;i&s;&s;ippi to Na&s;h|ville, is 2,250 dolls.</P>
<P>From Phila. to Na&s;hville as per letter R 6,300 dolls</P>
<P>In favor of the Mi&s;&s;i&s;&s;ippi commerce on every 25 tons weight. 4,050 dolls.</P>
<P>From the mouth of Ohio river, to the rapids, is about 475 miles&mdash;time of pa&s;&s;age to and from &s;aid ports, with a boat of 25 tons burthen, will be about 4<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> days; with the a&s;&s;i&s;tance of ten hands, at one dollar per day each, is 470 dollars</P>
