<P>The bearer hereof A B having de|livered to us the &s;um of <GAP DESC="blank" EXTENT="1 word"> dollars, This our bill certifies, that the &s;ame at the reque&s;t of the &s;aid A. B. is added to the Mi&s;&s;i&s;&s;ippi and Mobile commercial company's &s;tock' and &s;hall entitle him the &s;aid A. B. or his heirs, to all the profits, privileges, and advantages, &s;tipulated in the articles of the &s;aid company.</P>
<P>Art. 6 Cold, and &s;ilver coin, &s;hall be the &s;taple &s;ituation of all goods, wares, merchandize, and induce, advanced to be added to the company's
<PB N="16" REF="035360_0016_10049F62A2E94950">&s;tock; receivable at the current market prices.</P>
